# Insulin Glulisine

## Overview

Rapid-acting insulin analog with modified B-chain for enhanced monomer formation.

## Structure

| Property | Value |
| -------- | ----- |
| Name     | Insulin Glulisine |

## Mechanism of Action

Asparagine-B3 to lysine-B3 and lysine-B29 to asparagine-B29 substitutions prevent hexamer formation.

